# Infrastructure ({{ iac }})

IaC templates for deploying to **{{ runtime_display | default(runtime) }}**.

## Environments

- `dev`
- `stage`
- `prod`

Each environment uses separate config/parameter files. No shared production credentials with non-production.

## Deploy

Adjust parameters in the relevant env file, then apply:

{% if iac == "bicep" %}
```bash
az deployment group create --resource-group <rg> --template-file main.bicep --parameters @params.dev.json
```
{% elif iac == "terraform" %}
```bash
terraform init
terraform plan -var-file=dev.tfvars
terraform apply -var-file=dev.tfvars
```
{% endif %}
